{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>救援人員到場，發現姓馬（49歲）事主倒臥廁所，經檢查後，證實當場不治。警方檢獲約23粒懷疑含有依托咪酯（前稱太空油）煙彈，現正調查事件，稍後將驗屍確定其死因。</p><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260206/1096501181242413056723495.jpeg/ftxkRaaq73gBNDyV-acFKDpGrSY8XqHMYIxvZWCMb2U\"></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-23T08:52:01.717365+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":79,"images":1,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}